    "en": {
      "title": "Voice Teens Grand Finale tonight (3)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st);\u00a0Sri Lankans are facing challenging times at present.",
        "But even in these extremely difficult conditions, there\u2019s reason to celebrate the talent and skill of our young people.",
        "Sirasa, your family channel, brought down this globally franchised reality show, so that our young people can showcase their talent, on a global stage.",
        "Tonight, four young Sri Lankans will battle it out to win The Voice Teens Crown.",
        "Tonight, we will show the world, that Sri Lanka can and will, overcome, through the passion, grit and talent of our youth.",
        "Do not miss the Voice Teen Finals, on Sirasa TV this evening at 6 PM, when the red carpet will begin, and\u00a0the Live Competition will be held at 730 PM.",
        "The Finalists Are : Sasindu Raveen / Rasaal Theminda / Pranirsha Thiyagaraja / Navodya Perera.",
        "Yupun becomes first South Asian to finish 100m below 10 seconds & win"
      ],
